  "text": "Individuals with diabetes were excluded to avoid the confounding effects of treatment on HbA 1c . We defined diabetes as a fasting plasma glucose ≥ 7.0 mmol/L, report of a diagnosis of diabetes or use of hypoglycemic medications. HbA 1c levels were measured using HPLC (Bio-Rad DIA-MAT glycosylated hemoglobin analyzer system) [CITATION_1] .",
